                    	<note xml:id="n_dating" type="dating">
                    	    
<p xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">Vincent tells Theo about the letter he received from Marie Ginoux, dating from 10 June 1890, which announces that Vincent’s things will be sent on the coming Saturday (<ref target="let882.xml">letter 882</ref>). Since Van Gogh writes ‘Saturday, today in other words, they’d send it’ <ref target="#l-7">(ll. 7-8)</ref>, this must have been Saturday, 14 June. </p>
